    dc:description "FIGURES 30–34. Anapis nawchi n. sp. 30, Male palp retrolateral view. 30a, Male palp conductor and embolus, retrolateral view. 31, Male palp prolateral view. 32, Male chelicerae anterior view. 33, Male left metatarsus and tarsus I, prolateral view. 34, Male, left metatarsus and tarsus II, prolateral view." ;
